 hard to zoom or crop the image. The text is the most customizable feature on your photo card. The type is moveable, and you can adjust its size, font color and alignment. The photo card editor could use some extra features, but the site does have some interesting reference points to look at while you edit your batch. Above the editor, you can find etiquette and grammar advice when making cards for special occasions like weddings.","InvitationBox offers a few relatively rare features when compared to others in our photo cards review, such as the option to order your envelopes in advance. This feature is a great advantage if you place a large order and want to address the envelopes so that you can mail your cards as quickly as possible after your order arrives. All of your orders include envelopes, so you don&#39;t have to worry about any extra costs sneaking up on you. Most of the cards featured on the website also include a large-quantity discount, meaning that when you buy more cards, the price per card goes down.","However, we were disappointed to see that this service lacks a few features. For example, you can&#39;t save addresses or photos on your online account. InvitationBox offers proofs only after purchase, but your cards won&#39;t go to print until you&#39;ve approved what they&#39;ve sent you.","InvitationBox does have an extensive inventory, which is great, but with personalized photo cards specifically, the selection is much more limited. There is a strong selection of holiday photo cards, along with birth announcements and graduation cards. However, we couldn’t find any blank card templates, and the selection is limited for many of the less popular photo card options, such as response cards and new address announcements.","When it comes to customer support, this picture card service offers several options for contacting a company representative. Email, telephone and live chat support are all available. However, we tried to contact InvitationBox using live chat several times and never received a response."]},"id":"af0dca84-18f9-4cf2-80ac-522c25a6b2a1","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"11cd2277-1af0-4a06-a5dc-46133201112e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["InvitationBox lacks a few of the key features we value in the best photo card sites. Customization is limited to text features rather than photo editing like many other online card printing services. The good news is that InvitationBox has lovely cards that need little adjustment for your occasion. If you want a photo card service that can help you craft that perfectly worded message, InvitationBox is worth your consideration."]},"id":"b4e76ee3-1503-40ed-a45f-c85d72293027","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_52518","url":"/invitationbox-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"rebecca-spear","url":"/author/rebecca-spear","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Rebecca Spear","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"X8Ccy4LP9pMXtXdurbSshX","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2011-04-05T14:05:45Z","datePublished":"2011-04-05T14:05:45Z","name":"InvitationBox","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product.","review":{"rating":55,"verdict":"While the final product is quite nice with InvitationBox, competing services are easier to use.","pros":["The Wording Assistant can help you craft the message you want to share."],"cons":["Foil and embossing are missing from this site&#039;s photo card offerings."]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product.","language":"en","dateModified":"2011-04-05T14:05:45Z","id":"CoKP3xtGxe8jFtavhMWFWW","meta":{"title":"InvitationBox Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"See if InvitationBox is the right service for your photo card proj